item.description: today is a good day Uday Hussein’s house: The walls of a gym were plastered with photographs of women downloaded from the Internet - “the biggest collection of naked women I?d ever seen,” said US army Captain Ed Ballanco. “It looked like something at the Playboy Mansion.” Among the photos were those of Jenna and Barbara Bush, the president?s twin 21-year-old daughters, Ballanco said, adding that soldiers took them down “to protect the president.
